                <h1>Understanding Omnisexuality: A Comprehensive Guide</h1>
                <p>Omnisexuality embraces attraction to individuals regardless of their gender identity, highlighting a fluid approach to sexuality. Those identifying as omnisexual may find themselves attracted to men, women, non-binary, and genderqueer individuals alike. This perspective emphasizes love and connection over traditional labels.</p>
